{"tid":1167994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平機會真係垃圾嚟","createTime":"2019-05-23T11:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T12:05:57.000Z","uid":191815,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2737961680f89fbcfc09f62c1ccb2d9dd87a2c34","tid":1167994,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1459023-20190523.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1459023-20190523.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=6a715d31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1459023-20190523.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=464e33d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1459023-20190523.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>慈雲山醫館橫額稱向美遊客加收「關稅」　律師指或違法</strong><br />\n2019-05-23 HKT 18:39<br />\n<br />\n慈雲山一間醫館掛上橫額，表明向就診的美國籍遊客，加收25%「關稅」。<br />\n<br />\n海關表示，香港特區是一個自由港，進口及出口貨物均毋須繳付任何關稅，亦無任何關稅配額或附加稅。 <br />\n<br />\n大律師說，如果向不同國籍的客人徵收不同收費，可能違反種族歧視條例。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>平機會署理行政總裁朱崇文表示，盡量不想評論個別個案</ins>，但原則上歧視法律涵蓋膚色、世系及種族根源。<br />\n<br />\n咩叫盡量不想評論個別個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你全部個案都可以唔需要評論囉 乜都個別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874090a38f602faccf3812bec37219f19b3fd2e4","tid":1167994,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"驚呀嘛，出聲後果就係立法後第一個捉佢上去"},{"pid":"392817ee4f21d6447fc0a7bb33c9574cdbfd6eb1","tid":1167994,"uid":128991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"如果加收25%「關稅」嘅對象係支那人，平機會即刻仆出嚟譴責啦"},{"pid":"d86332c4199f69af67e6764543d324fbca6cb41f","tid":1167994,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"平機會只係可以處理「八婆」個案"},{"pid":"c291a9b483736e1e9a273e7929c550c32e5f6d6c","tid":1167994,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"胡志偉鬧「八婆」　平機會：以貶詞攻擊女性身份　有違男女平等<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1156201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1156201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e5c7d3465ddb8b1904405762e59caa0f563cb35d","tid":1167994,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"紅底平機會點敢郁愛共人士"}]}